        <updateDate>2004-11-22T20:39:17Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Requires the Attorney General and the Secretary of Homeland Security, using funds available for improving the national system to notify the public in the event of a terrorist attack, to conduct a pilot study under which the Secretary may issue public warnings regarding homeland security threats using an AMBER Alert system.</p> <p></p>]]></text>
      </summary>
